d\n- [ ] No issues found.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is excellent. The use of a 1.5x overhead factor provides a safe margin for unpredictable API costs. No further changes are required for this task.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-027@20260427t001208z-verify.md"}}
