uration file was provided in the repo.\\n\\n## Verdict: FAIL\\n\\n## Notes for Lead Agent\\nThe core audit logic and tests are perfect, but the systemd service cannot run as written. Please:\\n1. Update `cypherclaw-idyom-kl-audit.service` to include the necessary `PYTHONPATH`.\\n2. Either update `_main()` to read parameters directly from environment variables (matching its docstring and making the service truly declarative) OR update the service to point to a valid config file.\\n3. If using a JSON config file, provide a template (e.g., `my-claw/tools/senseweave/generation/idyom_kl_audit_config.json.example`).\\n\",\"file_path\":\"sdp/verification/t-031@20260427t001208z-verify.md\"}}\n+{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:08.786Z\",\"tool_id\":\"write_file_1777271468590_0\",\"status\":\"success\"}\n+{\"type\":\"message\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:12.001Z\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I've completed the verification. The core\",\"delta\":true}\n+{\"type\":\"message\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:12.024Z\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\" logic and tests are excellent, but the systemd service is non-functional due to missing environment variables and path configurations. I'\",\"delta\":true}\n+{\"type\":\"message\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:12.040Z\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"ve documented these blocking issues in the verification report. Per the task instructions, I will now commit this report.\\n\\n\",\"delta\":true}\n+{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:12.077Z\",\"tool_name\":\"run_shell_command\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1777271472077_0\",\"parameters\":{\"command\":\"git add sdp/verification/t-031@20260427t001208z-verify.md && git commit -m \\\"verify(T-031@20260427T001208Z): FAIL\\\"\",\"description\":\"Commit the verification report for T-031.\"}}\n+[AGENT] Elapsed: 2m 32s / 30m 0s\n+{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-27T06:31:12.460Z\",\"tool_id\":\"run_